ize":20,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1775542838742,"locked":false,"text":"인증 흐름","version":2,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","roundness":null,"index":"ag","containerId":null,"originalText":"인증 흐름","height":25,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":1628001074,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":1,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":30,"angle":0,"y":790,"width":200},{"seed":303,"strokeStyle":"solid","id":"legend-content","strokeWidth":2,"roughness":0,"isDeleted":false,"fontSize":14,"opacity":100,"verticalAlign":"top","updated":1775542838742,"locked":false,"text":"① User 로그인: User → Gateway → Auth → Google OAuth → User JWT (1h, RS256)\n② Provider 등록: User(JWT) → Gateway → Auth(\/auth\/provider\/register) → PENDING [이번 구현]\n③ Provider 토큰: User(JWT) → Gateway → Auth(\/auth\/provider\/token) → Provider JWT (90d) [이번 구현]\n④ Gateway 인증: Gateway → Auth(\/validate) → X-User-Id 헤더 주입 → 백엔드 [향후]\n⑤ Kafka 토큰: Agent(Provider JWT) → Auth → Kafka Access Token (1h) [향후]\n⑥ Agent 통신: Agent → Kafka (SASL OAUTHBEARER) [향후]\n⑦ Kafka 검증: Kafka → Auth(JWKS) 공개키 캐시 [향후]\n\n파란색: User JWT  주황색: Provider JWT  분홍색: Kafka Token  보라색: 신뢰 헤더  회색: 인증 없음","version":2,"autoResize":true,"type":"text","backgroundColor":"transparent","roundness":null,"index":"ah","containerId":null,"originalText":"① User 로그인: User → Gateway → Auth → Google OAuth → User JWT (1h, RS256)\n② Provider 등록: User(JWT) → Gateway → Auth(\/auth\/provider\/register) → PENDING [이번 구현]\n③ Provider 토큰: User(JWT) → Gateway → Auth(\/auth\/provider\/token) → Provider JWT (90d) [이번 구현]\n④ Gateway 인증: Gateway → Auth(\/validate) → X-User-Id 헤더 주입 → 백엔드 [향후]\n⑤ Kafka 토큰: Agent(Provider JWT) → Auth → Kafka Access Token (1h) [향후]\n⑥ Agent 통신: Agent → Kafka (SASL OAUTHBEARER) [향후]\n⑦ Kafka 검증: Kafka → Auth(JWKS) 공개키 캐시 [향후]\n\n파란색: User JWT  주황색: Provider JWT  분홍색: Kafka Token  보라색: 신뢰 헤더  회색: 인증 없음","height":200,"link":null,"strokeColor":"#1e1e1e","fillStyle":"solid","groupIds":[],"versionNonce":223228142,"textAlign":"left","fontFamily":1,"lineHeight":1.25,"frameId":null,"boundElements":[],"x":30,"angle":0,"y":825,"width":700}],"source":"hand-crafted","files":{}}